      "key": "httpSuccessRate",
      "name": "HTTP Success Rate",
      "description": "### What is the expected success rate of HTTP requests while Redis has high latency?\n\nFinding an appropriate success rate usually depends on the offered service's business criticality and retry mechanisms in place. If the service is, e.g., called by another application with an appropriate retry mechanism, the success rate may be lower compared to a user-visible endpoint."
    }
